#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:2
msgid "Generic Wrappers"
msgstr "泛型包装器"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:5
msgid "Wrap a Specific Method, Function, Behaviour"
msgstr "包装特定方法、函数、行为"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:7
msgid ""
"With the power of non-type template parameter (NTTP), asbind20 can "
"generate generic wrapper of any function by macro-free utilities. "
"Additionally, it supports wrapping a function with variable type "
"(declared by ``?`` in the AngelScript)."
msgstr ""
"借助非类型模板参数（NTTP）的能力，asbind20 可以通过无需宏的工具"
"为任何函数生成泛型包装器。"
"此外，它还支持包装具有可变类型（在 AngelScript 中由 ``?`` 声明）的函数。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:11
msgid ""
"This can be useful for binding interface on platform without native "
"calling convention support, e.g., Emscripten."
msgstr ""
"这对于在没有原生调用约定支持的平台上绑定接口非常有用，"
"例如 Emscripten。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:15
msgid ""
"Besides, generic calling convention might have better performance than "
"native calling convention when binding functions of shorter parameter "
"list, but this is platform dependent. You can check benchmarks of "
"asbind20 to decide whether to prefer using generic calling convention."
msgstr ""
"此外，在绑定参数列表较短的函数时，泛型调用约定可能比原生调用约定"
"具有更好的性能，但这取决于平台。"
"你可以查看 asbind20 的基准测试来决定是否优先使用泛型调用约定。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:20
msgid "Global Functions"
msgstr "全局函数"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:22
msgid ""
"Due to the limitation of C++, you need to pass the function pointer by "
"the helper ``fp<>``. But lambda expression still can be directly "
"registered."
msgstr ""
"由于 C++ 的限制，你需要通过辅助工具 ``fp<>`` 传递函数指针。"
"但 lambda 表达式仍然可以直接注册。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:50
msgid "Ordinary Methods and Behaviours"
msgstr "普通方法和行为"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:52
msgid ""
"Generic wrappers for methods and behaviours are generated in the similar "
"way."
msgstr "方法和行为的泛型包装器以类似的方式生成。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:76
msgid "Functions with Variable Type Argument"
msgstr "具有可变类型参数的函数"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:78
msgid ""
"Functions with variable type argument receive the variable parameter "
"(``?``) from AngelScript by a pair of ``void*`` and ``int``. The first "
"one contains address of argument, while the second one contains the type "
"ID."
msgstr ""
"具有可变类型参数的函数通过一对 ``void*`` 和 ``int``"
"从 AngelScript 接收可变参数（``?``）。"
"前者包含参数的地址，后者包含类型 ID。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:81
msgid ""
"The helper ``var_type<Is...>`` needs the indices of ``?`` in **script** "
"parameter list."
msgstr ""
"辅助工具 ``var_type<Is...>`` 需要 ``?`` 在**脚本**参数列表中的索引。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:83
msgid "Examples"
msgstr "示例"

