#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:135
msgid "Wrapping Composite Methods"
msgstr "包装组合方法"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:137
msgid ""
"The interface of AngelScript only accepts ``THISCALL`` for the composite "
"methods, which means the generic wrapper should take the composite offset"
" into consideration at compile-time. If you want to generate generic "
"wrapper for composite methods, you need to tell the generator how to "
"access the composite data."
msgstr ""
"AngelScript 的接口对组合方法只接受 ``THISCALL``，"
"这意味着泛型包装器需要在编译时考虑组合偏移量。"
"如果你想为组合方法生成泛型包装器，"
"你需要告诉生成器如何访问组合数据。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:142
msgid ""
"The major difference from the native one is how to use the ``composite`` "
"helper."
msgstr ""
"与原生方式的主要区别在于如何使用 ``composite`` 辅助工具。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:173
msgid "Wrap a Group of Methods, Functions, or Behaviours"
msgstr "包装一组方法、函数或行为"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:175
msgid ""
"If you want to force a group of registered functions to be generic, you "
"can set the ``ForceGeneric`` flag of binding generator to ``true``. You "
"can use this flag to avoid the code for registering the application "
"interface being flooded by ``use_generic``."
msgstr ""
"如果你想强制一组注册的函数使用泛型，"
"可以将绑定生成器的 ``ForceGeneric`` 标志设置为 ``true``。"
"你可以使用此标志来避免注册应用接口的代码中充斥大量 ``use_generic``。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:185
msgid ""
"Trying to register functions by native calling convention with "
"``ForceGeneric`` enabled will trigger a compile-time error. If you are "
"targeting a platform without native calling convention support by "
"AngelScript, this flag can be helpful to discover bugs early."
msgstr ""
"在启用 ``ForceGeneric`` 的情况下尝试通过原生调用约定注册函数"
"将触发编译时错误。"
"如果你的目标平台不受 AngelScript 的原生调用约定支持，"
"此标志有助于及早发现错误。"

#: ../../doc/advanced/generic.rst:190
msgid ""
"If you use an outer template argument to control the mode of binding "
"generator, the generator will be a dependent name, thus you need an "
"additional ``template`` disambiguator to use the binding generator."
msgstr ""
"如果你使用外部模板参数来控制绑定生成器的模式，"
"生成器将成为依赖名称，"
"因此你需要额外的 ``template`` 消歧符来使用绑定生成器。"

